# variantconvert

Usage instructions:
1) create an appropriate python env with python>=3.8 ; panda and pyfaidx ; or use the python from the dockerfile
2) git clone the project
3) cd variantconvert
4) pip install -e .
5) change the genome path in config files

For more info:
variantconvert --help
